==English==

===Acronym===
'''PAN'''

# '''P'''rimary '''A'''ccount '''N'''umber


With reference to financial industry web sites, such as APACS, UK, this is simply the account number found embossed on plastic cards. It has a maximum length of 19 digits and is made up of three parts: 6 digits to identify the Issuer (IIN), up to 12 digits for the account number and a single check digit at the end.

